                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18110529-118-off678 t18110529-118-cd679"></join>, a saddle, value 1 l. and a bridle, value 5 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18110529-118-victim957" type="victimName">
                     Edward 
                     Ledger
                  <interp inst="t18110529-118-victim957" type="surname" value="Ledger"></interp>
